data.description: Country living at its finest! Great location, this home is nestled in off the beaten path, situated in a cul-de-sac on a .77 acre, level lot. The Main Level features an open floor plan, LR w/bow window & brand new wall to wall carpeting, the Eat-in-Kitchen w/dining area, propane fueled fireplace, center island w/seating, granite countertops & entrance out to the bonus Sun Room w/propane heater & sliders out to the Trex Deck & inground saltwater pool, Koi pond w/waterfall, gorgeous landscaping once Spring, Summer & Fall come around. Plenty of room for family, friends & pets to frolic around, includes invisible fence w/2 collars for cost savings! Primary Suite offers walk-in-closet & full bath. 2 more Bdrms w/new carpeting, a Full Bath & attic w/pull down stairs & fan complete the Main Level. Ceiling fans in every room on Main Level will keep you cool. The LL is finished, heated and offers a separate room w/half bath, laundry hookup & heated garage access. New Hot Water Heater. Large cement pad for trailer or boat w/electric hookup! Subject to seller finding & closing on rent of choice. Inspections STRICTLY for INFORMATIONAL PURPOSES ONLY! Room sizes are approx. Pool has been professionally opened & closed since it was put in. Seller prefers CTR/GHAR Contract. Schedule your showing today!
